text: Leuwiliang is a town and district in the province of West Java on Java in Indonesia. Currently it lies within Bogor Regency, but is within that part of the regency that is being split off to form the new West Bogor Regency. The population according to the 2010 census was 113,280;Indonesian Center of Statistics the official estimate (as at 2017) was 122,352.Badan Pusat Statistik, Jakarta, 2019. ==References== Category:Districts of Bogor Regency Category:Populated places in West Java
